  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will explore barriers in the process of achieving informed consent from critically
      ill patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The barriers will be divided into four major categories:

        -  Practical barriers

        -  Medical barriers

        -  Legal barriers

        -  Ethical barriers
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
